Start the server

Usage:
  jobly server [--port NUMBER --bind IP --daemonize]
  jobly server stop
  jobly server (-h|--help)

Commands:
  stop
    Stop a previously started daemonized server

Options:
  -b, --bind IP
    Set the listen address [default: 0.0.0.0]

  -p, --port NUMBER
    Set the port number [default: 3000]

  -d, --daemonize
    Run in the background

  -h --help
    Show this help

Examples:
  jobly server -d
  jobly server --port 4567 --daemonize
  jobly server stop
